{"tid":1312051,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(代po) 作為上水居民 我衷心代表北區人多謝大家","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T12:26:18.000Z","uid":20294,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"608f2cfad0b3f0fdb55bd5ec1f5d4e652a90eb31","tid":1312051,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"北區水貨情況令我地苦不堪言<br />\n今日大家黎支持我地 <br />\n清曬啲烏煙障氣既鋪頭<br />\n唔知效果幾長<br />\n左要比佢地知 <br />\n我地唔好恰<br />\n<br />\n今日既上水 先係我細個見到既上水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LZQZc6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LZQZc6.png&h=ed926ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然班狗無性 又打女人 又打記者<br />\n但呢仇 唔係今日 可以報 <br />\n要同佢長期戰<br />\n同埋上水 都無戰略價值 去做任何防務<br />\n<br />\n所以 我懇請大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BE WATER.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再想衷心講一句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝大家</span></span>"},{"pid":"4cc6de0e28b9755971efbbc7f250a581bfeb3bec","tid":1312051,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:11:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85b9dcae1f087d29abc614d9750ee37e6d19bc6","tid":1312051,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90d0ab67e34420d29048cf89d53035b5d5717571","tid":1312051,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"一方有難 八方支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12f13d8eeb6234b96d04e50fca79b16e08a60f8","tid":1312051,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"14900e23fe06c79c28fa6e5fef0fb5a1bcc10dfa","tid":1312051,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e54715bea32c3af5f848c59e4bf17334d907fba1","tid":1312051,"